nightshade
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:6
Definition:a. mistakenly =black nightshade usually applied to <i>Solanum</i> sp(p), BLACK NIGHTSHADE, but in Rotorua-Taupo district it is sometimes applied to <i>Leycesteria formosa </i>
Origin:
